						<summary>

						<p>Stone set up in the north Māḍa street.</p>						

						<p>It mentions certain individuals Yedurukoṇḍa Jaḍa Rāmappanāyanivāru, Bangāru Virappanāyanivāru Timma Nāyanivāru and also record the gift of 100 <hi rend="italic">kuṉtas</hi> of land in the village. Other details are not known. In late characters.</p>						

						</summary>
