<lb n="1"/>maḍimānyaṁ 
<lb n="2"/>100 guṁṭṭalu 
<lb n="3"/>pai yī <unclear>grāmaṁ</unclear> 
<lb n="4"/>lō rūkalu 
<lb n="5"/>40 dhara 
